videos.headline: Colorado's Clayton punches in a pair of short TDs in the 2nd
videos.description: Ashaad Clayton rushes for two short touchdowns in the second quarter to put Colorado up 14-13 heading to the half vs. Arizona.

videos.headline: Arizona's Casteel reaches back for incredible snag
